    "This broader educational framework could provide additional insights and methodologies for professional development programs, as suggested by recent literature (Erduran and Cheung, 2024; Rehman et al. 2021).",
    "Incorporating STEAM into China's educational framework could enhance the impact of professional development by fostering a more interdisciplinary and innovative teaching approach.",
    "This approach aligns with the goals of the existing TPD programs, which emphasize the integration of multiple disciplines and the application of creative problemsolving strategies in educational practice.",
    "Moreover, STEAM could address some of the limitations identified in current TPD practices, such as the need for more diverse and engaging pedagogical approaches.",
